==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Obstructive
<hw>Ob*struct"ive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>obstrictif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Tending to obstruct; presenting
obstacles; hindering; causing impediment.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Ob*struct"ive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obstructive</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Obstructive
<hw>Ob*struct"ive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An obstructive person or
thing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Obstruent</ent>⟦br⟧
